privacy_policy:
{name} wakhe uhlelo lokusebenza iJot njengohlelo lokusebenza lwamahhala Le SEVISI inikezwa ngu- {name} mahhala futhi yenzelwe ukusetshenziswa njengoba injalo.

Lokhu kwenzelwa ukwazisa abasebenzisi mayelana nezinqubomgomo zami ngokuqoqwa, ukusetshenziswa, kanye nokudalulwa Kwemininingwane yomuntu uma noma ngubani ethatha isinqumo sokusebenzisa i-Service yami.

Uma ukhetha ukusebenzisa i-Service yami, khona-ke uyavuma ukuqoqwa nokusetshenziswa kolwazi maqondana nale nqubomgomo. Ngeke ngisebenzise noma ngabelane ngemininingwane yakho nanoma ngubani ngaphandle kwalapho kuchazwe kule Nqubomgomo Yobumfihlo.


** Ukuqoqwa Kwemininingwane Nokusebenzisa **

Ukuhlangenwe nakho okungcono, ngenkathi ngisebenzisa Isevisi yethu, ngingahle ngidinge ukuthi usinikeze imininingwane ethile ekhomba umuntu uqobo, kufaka phakathi kepha kungagcini ngegama lomsebenzisi ne-imeyili. Imininingwane engiyicelayo izogcinwa kudivayisi yakho futhi ayiqoqwa yimina nganoma iyiphi indlela.

Uhlelo lokusebenza lusebenzisa amasevisi wesithathu angaqoqa imininingwane esetshenziselwe ukukukhomba.

Xhuma kunqubomgomo yobumfihlo yabahlinzeki benkampani yangaphandle esetshenziswa uhlelo lokusebenza

* [Google Play Services] (https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/)

* [I-Google Analytics yeFirebase] (https://firebase.google.com/policies/analytics)


** Log Idatha **

Ngifuna ukukwazisa ukuthi noma nini lapho usebenzisa i-Service yami, uma kwenzeka kuba nephutha kuhlelo lokusebenza ngiqoqa idatha nemininingwane (ngemikhiqizo yomuntu wesithathu) efonini yakho ebizwa nge-Log Data. Le Log Data ingafaka imininingwane efana nekheli ledivayisi yakho ye-Internet Protocol (“IP”), igama ledivayisi, inguqulo yesistimu yokusebenza, ukumiswa kohlelo lokusebenza lapho usebenzisa i-Service yami, isikhathi nosuku lokusebenzisa kwakho isevisi, nezinye izibalo .


** Abahlinzeki Bezinsizakalo **

Ngingaqasha izinkampani ezivela eceleni nabantu ngazinye ngenxa yalezi zizathu ezilandelayo:

* Ukwenza lula Insizakalo yethu;

* Ukuhlinzeka ngemisebenzi esikhundleni sethu;

* Ukwenza izinsizakalo ezihlobene Nensizakalo; noma

* Ukusisiza ekuhlaziyeni ukuthi isevisi yethu isetshenziswa kanjani.

Ngifuna ukwazisa abasebenzisi bale sevisi ukuthi laba bantu besithathu bayakwazi ukuthola imininingwane yakho. Isizathu ukwenza imisebenzi abayabelwe thina. Kodwa-ke, babophezelekile ukuthi bangadaluli noma basebenzise imininingwane nganoma iyiphi enye injongo.


** Ezokuphepha **

Ngiyakwazisa ukuthembela kwakho ekusinikeni imininingwane yakho, ngakho-ke silwela ukusebenzisa izindlela ezamukelekayo zokuyivikela. Kepha khumbula ukuthi ayikho indlela yokudlulisa nge-inthanethi, noma indlela yokugcina ngogesi ephephe nge-100% futhi ethembekile, futhi angikwazi ukuqinisekisa ukuphepha kwayo ngokuphelele.


** Izinguquko Kule Nqubomgomo Yobumfihlo **

Ngingahle ngibuyekeze inqubomgomo yethu yobumfihlo ngezikhathi ezithile. Ngakho-ke, welulekwa ukuthi ubuyekeze leli khasi ngezikhathi ezithile nganoma yiziphi izinguquko. Ngizokwazisa nganoma yiziphi izinguquko ngokuthumela Inqubomgomo Yemfihlo entsha kuleli khasi.
